
Multiple Creatures Saving Throws vs DC
Total Number of Saves = [[{?{Number Of Creatures Saving}d20+?{Saving Bonus}}>?{DC}]]
# Creature Saving: ?{Number Of Creatures Saving}
With a Saving Bonus Of: 1d20+?{Saving Bonus}
VS A DC of: ?{DC}

Mutliple Creature(s)/Attack(s) vs Single Target (To Hit)
Total Number Of Hits = [[{?{Number Of Creature(s) or/and Attack(s)}d20+?{Attack Bonus}}>?{Target AC}]]
# of Creatures Attacking: ?{Number Of Creature(s) or/and Attack(s)}
Attack Bonus: ?{Attack Bonus} vs Target AC: ?{Target AC}

Mutliple Creature(s)/Attack(s) vs Single Target (Damage)
Total Damage = [[{?{Number Of Creature(s)/Attack(s) That Hit}d?{Damage Dice Sides}+?{Number Of Creature(s)/Attack(s) That Hit}*?{Damage Bonus}}]]
# of Creatures Hit: ?{Number Of Creature(s)/Attack(s) That Hit}
Damage Dice Sides: ?{Damage Dice Sides} Damage Bonus: ?{Damage Bonus}

